&lt;ul>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>Critical インシデント&lt;/strong>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>料金</title><link>https://bpinelab.github.io/doc-template/service/price/</link><pubDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://bpinelab.github.io/doc-template/service/price/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="1-料金概要">1. 料金概要&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#1-%e6%96%99%e9%87%91%e6%a6%82%e8%a6%81" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
